# Title: Suspicious X509Enrollment - Process Creation
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-12-23
# Level: medium
# Description: Detect use of X509Enrollment
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1553.004
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_powershell_x509enrollment.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate administrative script

CommandLine IN ("*X509Enrollment.CBinaryConverter*", "*884e2002-217d-11da-b2a4-000e7bbb2b09*")